patthana23.21:1.1_0: Navipākaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā vipākadhammadhammo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.21:2.1_0: Navipākaṁ naakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā vipākadhammadhammo akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.21:3.1_0: Navipākaṁ naabyākataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nevavipākanavipākadhammadhammo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
